[
    {
        "text": "If you think living on Earth can be challenging,...",
        "startTime": 3617,
        "endTime": 5585,
        "slowStartTime": 5576,
        "slowEndTime": 8603
    },
    {
        "text": "...try spending a day on 55 Cancri e.",
        "startTime": 5780,
        "endTime": 8322,
        "slowStartTime": 8820,
        "slowEndTime": 12708
    },
    {
        "text": "The super-Earth is located about 40 light years from here...",
        "startTime": 8938,
        "endTime": 11955,
        "slowStartTime": 13557,
        "slowEndTime": 18157
    },
    {
        "text": "...and at least half of it is lightly covered in blazing hot lava.",
        "startTime": 12351,
        "endTime": 15921,
        "slowStartTime": 18677,
        "slowEndTime": 24107
    },
    {
        "text": "Temperatures can hover upwards of 4,400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
        "startTime": 16393,
        "endTime": 20283,
        "slowStartTime": 24739,
        "slowEndTime": 30650
    },
    {
        "text": "Part of the heat problem is due to the exoplanet's incredibly close proximity to its sun.",
        "startTime": 20784,
        "endTime": 25034,
        "slowStartTime": 31326,
        "slowEndTime": 37776
    },
    {
        "text": "The issue is particularly pronounced on one side of the celestial body,...",
        "startTime": 25438,
        "endTime": 29108,
        "slowStartTime": 38307,
        "slowEndTime": 43887
    },
    {
        "text": "...as astronomers believe it is tidally locked to the star,...",
        "startTime": 29460,
        "endTime": 32159,
        "slowStartTime": 44340,
        "slowEndTime": 48464
    },
    {
        "text": "...much like our moon is to Earth.",
        "startTime": 32516,
        "endTime": 34135,
        "slowStartTime": 48924,
        "slowEndTime": 51428
    },
    {
        "text": "That means 1/2 is forever exposed, while the other remains eternally dark.",
        "startTime": 34580,
        "endTime": 38905,
        "slowStartTime": 52020,
        "slowEndTime": 58582
    },
    {
        "text": "Unfortunately, that doesn't prevent the dark side...",
        "startTime": 39388,
        "endTime": 41383,
        "slowStartTime": 59232,
        "slowEndTime": 62299
    },
    {
        "text": "...from having temperature issues as well.",
        "startTime": 41476,
        "endTime": 43152,
        "slowStartTime": 62364,
        "slowEndTime": 64953
    },
    {
        "text": "Researchers estimate it's still a bit over 2,000 degrees Fahrenheit there.",
        "startTime": 43501,
        "endTime": 47637,
        "slowStartTime": 65402,
        "slowEndTime": 71680
    }
]